ns."}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ViewStore","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"ViewStore","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ViewStore"}]},"doc://ComposableArchitecture/documentation/ComposableArchitecture/SwiftUIIntegration":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/SwiftUIIntegration","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/swiftuiintegration","abstract":[{"text":"Integrating the Composable Architecture into a SwiftUI application.","type":"text"}],"role":"collectionGroup","type":"topic","title":"SwiftUI Integration"}}}